videos.description: Reid Travis gets the dish from Daejon Davis and sinks the 3-pointer in the first half.
videos.headline: Stanford's Travis drills 3-pointer

videos.description: Reid Travis posts up his defender and makes the turnaround-jumper through contact.
videos.headline: Stanford's Travis hits tough and-1 layup

videos.description: Luke Maye gets his defender to jump, then hits the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: UNC's Maye displays beautiful post moves

videos.description: Joel Berry II puts the moves on his defender, steps back and hits the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: UNC's Berry sinks 3-pointer

videos.description: Oscar da Silva finishes the layup through contact after getting the full-court pass.
videos.headline: Stanford's da Silva receives full-court pass, lays it in

videos.description: Reid Travis lays down the hammer on UNC in the second half.
videos.headline: Stanford's Travis throws down monster dunk

videos.description: Jalek Felton rocks the rim late in the game to cap off a big win over Stanford for UNC.
videos.headline: Felton caps off win with poster dunk
